rComments: Used kahoots as a grading method and made the time to answer too short for long complicated questions

Professor Sara is a genuine professor and you can tell she cares about what she is teaching. She brings forward great energy when it comes to her lectures and enjoys when the class participates. She makes 3 hour lectures seem quick and she is good at getting to the point and explaining the essentials.
She is very nice and cares about her students. Class participation is necessary.
